  "name": "Building Blocks - DDE Building Blocks repository",
  "abstract": "Building blocks for Deep-time Digital Earth (DDE) metadata profiles,\nusing the OGC Building Blocks pattern.\n",
  "description": "Modular schema components for DDE resource type metadata. Imports shared\nschema.org and CDIF property building blocks from the CDIF Building Blocks repository.\n",
  "modified": "2026-03-16T22:53:22.193703",
